</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"e16bf7a8cdae">All steps must be explicit, actionable, and or=
dered.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"52d0f190662b" id=3D"RapidRecoveryInformationHub-6.2Required=
ContentSections">6.2 Required Content Sections</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"a977219c-901d-49b5-bc65-2c18bcb3f664">
<li local-id=3D"34f16e08-1401-43cf-a442-94cacd5920f5">
<p local-id=3D"213d7be0942c">Application taxonomy &amp; integrations</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"58f15e0e-c6e0-4ad6-a028-c9ea0e512002">
<p local-id=3D"db3aac6a3e4b">Technology stack and support groups</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8d20ed63-5057-46bf-9dbb-617da1794adf">
<p local-id=3D"ee61addaf3e2">Detailed triage and recovery sequence</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"92fe4d91-2b4e-484c-82b9-37cfdbbe2aeb">
<p local-id=3D"18cb969cc3bd">Vendor and third=E2=80=91party coordination</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"137f59ea-7267-42c9-8de9-269666bb291e">
<p local-id=3D"4e84e964f631">RTO and impact considerations</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a08c55e5-1461-4f92-85ca-3369575a5ade">
<p local-id=3D"324481f3e62d">Contacts and appendices</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"45a7f42fd281" id=3D"RapidRecoveryInformationHub-6.3Document=
Control">6.3 Document Control</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"d813c853-e4dd-4932-b75e-1e798d35e258">
<li local-id=3D"6d95edf4-e369-4904-927f-928528acfd69">
<p local-id=3D"5b0cb048ebf7">Version history</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"59572075-78fc-43dd-be7d-85804a4f0f55">
<p local-id=3D"af0ff2529dbf">Review cadence</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ce2bb0bf-24ba-4aba-8c9c-e7be983840ff">
<p local-id=3D"61e78e2df81c">Identification of major / medium / minor updat=
es</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"d746eb1c-7817-4e48-8009-c1417ed8df62">
<h2 local-id=3D"523feecb5550" id=3D"RapidRecoveryInformationHub-7.Registeri=
ngtheRRP(Mandatory)">7. Registering the RRP (Mandatory)</h2>
<p local-id=3D"fbe1f8a0f142">Once prepared, <strong>every RRP must be regis=
tered</strong> as a <strong>ServiceNow Knowledge Article</strong> using:</p=
>
<blockquote local-id=3D"6e950a62-8615-4926-8b7b-db21ef93e023">
<p local-id=3D"775687b4177e"><strong>Create Rapid Recovery Plan (RRP) Knowl=
edge Article =E2=80=93 myServices</strong></p>
</blockquote>
<p local-id=3D"a00bd7f30c5d">Minimum registration requirements:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"86c1cabe-b482-4f14-963e-6c48150b15ef">
<li local-id=3D"48f6ea67-fafd-468c-83c8-f2e1ec4999e5">
<p local-id=3D"56f2c9c5f572">Correct <strong>Application / CI reference</st=
rong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1b78994d-9f17-4777-998e-a5f47ece0e77">
<p local-id=3D"d256e8dac540">Knowledge Base =3D ITIL Knowledge</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2b45110f-782e-4e53-bce6-d45a812d9d42">
<p local-id=3D"2a6a5e29086b">Category =3D Global RRP</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"58cac800-72e9-44b7-99a2-b8bb0020b037">
<p local-id=3D"a0b9db94e26e">Valid Through date set</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f221756d-78c9-4a84-860b-d66974a63573">
<p local-id=3D"f8286ec11781">All required sections populated (not placehold=
ers)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"4ed5343e75f0">The Knowledge Article is the <strong>system of=
 record</strong> for RRP compliance and reporting.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"50e0b034-28a6-4d7e-ab0f-bf36ec757fd7">
<h2 local-id=3D"2221c9e885c3" id=3D"RapidRecoveryInformationHub-8.UsingInge=
niumasthePattern">8. Using Ingenium as the Pattern</h2>
<p local-id=3D"d9b8eee2c18d">Ingenium is the <strong>first standardized imp=
lementation</strong>. For other MLJ internal applications:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"6c45fed9-b37a-4581-90fa-a1a326c14e6e">
<li local-id=3D"e437d383-268f-4602-9c32-ee18397474d8">
<p local-id=3D"2fa0e1db8d52">Reuse the same structure and level of detail</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5a217f61-7085-4f7b-89a9-4c5301522bf9">
<p local-id=3D"5cea15f12e15">Adapt recovery steps to the application=E2=80=
=99s architecture</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ad004436-1014-45ae-9b78-f8d0611be0a5">
<p local-id=3D"67f1f9bf1b1a">Register each RRP individually</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"af9b504a-db81-4ed4-9ea6-6ec61bb68a85">
<p local-id=3D"1b4f94ed7b3f">Keep recovery instructions operational (not th=
eoretical)</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"46aa5c5e462f">Consistency across apps is critical for scale,=
 governance, and future automation.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"893301fe-fc45-4f47-930c-1d9fc4896d9e">
<h2 local-id=3D"0a50e9f3015f" id=3D"RapidRecoveryInformationHub-9.Ownership=
&amp;Expectations">9. Ownership &amp; Expectations</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"14bd3043-f4ac-4b9f-a6e9-a31e5706fd5b">
<li local-id=3D"9c89f607-c980-40cb-9906-74b723b83624">
<p local-id=3D"47f4c7105191"><strong>Prod Support</strong>: Execute Rapid R=
ecovery during incidents</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2bc35d45-e870-4da2-8006-154ff8bb7f9f">
<p local-id=3D"268ad3e00a2b"><strong>Application Owners / SMEs</strong>: De=
fine accurate recovery steps</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e7382ea2-9eee-40d7-b7fc-a97aa386561a">
<p local-id=3D"68d8ad1e6dbf"><strong>Registrars</strong>: Ensure RRP Knowle=
dge Articles are complete and current</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"0adfcbe58ccb">Rapid Recovery documentation is <strong>operat=
ional infrastructure</strong>, not optional documentation.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"0b6fc72a-20ad-466e-9b78-c4e0e71a2f67">
